questions.title: Bees are in my couch?
questions.author: Ted Cruz
questions.detail: They buzz and buzz. It hurts.

questions.title: My head is too big?
questions.author: Barack Obama
questions.detail: I think I have a head. It might be big.

questions.title: Why are hats?
questions.author: Hillary Clinton
questions.detail: Are hats? If so, why? Are hats for heads?

questions.title: Pizza is a vegetable?
questions.author: Donald Trump
questions.detail: I eat pizza and tacos and donuts in milk.
